# Stage 02 — design (L2)

Detailed technical design from the scope refined in discovery. Produces `plan.md` in the 4-block schema + Files touched + ADRs per task (wave-planner runs inline in this stage, v4.0). Creates new ADRs in `{{PROJECT_ROOT}}/.icm-main/docs/decisions/` (worktree linked to the base branch) when architectural decisions arise (stack, db, dependencies, paid services, irreversible migrations, etc.). Human gate before transitioning to stage 04 (implementation waves).

